{"tid":485052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呂麗瑤婉拒與警方合作(2)","createTime":"2017-11-30T15:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T06:12:39.000Z","uid":47359,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"344c98f948a702b4604b86a823f7280dd72401d1","tid":485052,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:17:00.000Z","msg":"港隊「欄后」呂麗瑤在網上自爆中學時曾遭校隊教練性侵，據悉警方今日已間接接觸她，但她婉拒與警方合作。消息指，由於這宗懷疑性侵案暫無任何人證物證或環境證據，警方需當事人合作舉報才可展開調查，故會繼續派人嘗試聯絡呂麗瑤游說她報警，並不排除到呂就讀的培正中學調查。"},{"pid":"00e064c5b0586b19103ff48dec2bac31085d2b5c","tid":485052,"uid":22858,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>經crosscheck多個post，最新確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: red;\">三色貓</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">法國佬巫斯義</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">極右派政治家</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Coffee@</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Gladiclus</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">newlife</span></del>、JR、RedBaron = Epiphany、dewi、bbchu、D_Wade、Spurs_Leonard、十卜Ching、侵B、民國復興、群龍共舞、霍金轉身、優美開始、黑腸盧卡庫 = 國語好手、返六日唔撚易、追捕兩米黑鬼、吾系甘開心牙、社會主義者佛利民、小翁翁、毛澤東、晚媚</strong></span>"},{"pid":"769c1aa12d455cbb779f5abac094332312cca5b3","tid":485052,"uid":47359,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:18:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持呂麗瑤報警<br />\n以免兇徒逍遙法外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"a5895a659b4b11e95c510bb38a199339209349e7","tid":485052,"uid":31887,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:18:21.000Z","msg":"欄后玩爛玩後欄"},{"pid":"24e7d8ae333109218fca56f45d93d51ccd8c155e","tid":485052,"uid":47359,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">夠膽fb公開事件<br />\n唔夠膽落口供係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"be1ce4365e1a27097ff06d129127a435d2f17df1","tid":485052,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>欄后玩爛玩後欄</blockquote><br />\n呢個新嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4a6d29a9e793e288c30bb78a742d1f2106b904","tid":485052,"uid":35221,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:20:34.000Z","msg":"又唔post link，班盲撚又會屌關愛座兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n==<br />\n【體壇性侵】警下午抵培正搜集資料 林鄭籲呂麗瑤報警<br />\n最後更新: 1130 18:52 / 建立時間 (HKT): 1130 15:56<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171130/large/1512040517_4946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171130%2Flarge%2F1512040517_4946.jpg&h=d6b112e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171130/large/1512033200_ac90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171130%2Flarge%2F1512033200_ac90.jpg&h=3469bb58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（馬泉崇攝 ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171130/large/1512032464_00ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171130%2Flarge%2F1512032464_00ab.jpg&h=b51af761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（馬泉崇攝 ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【新增影片】<br />\n港隊「欄后」呂麗瑤在網上自爆中學時曾遭校隊教練性侵，警方下午派人到呂的母校培正中學，四名便裝探員到場後，未有回應記者提問。據悉，警方今日已間接接觸過呂麗瑤，但她婉拒與警方合作。消息指，由於這宗懷疑性侵案暫無任何人證物證或環境證據，警方需當事人合作舉報才可展開調查，故會繼續派人嘗試聯絡呂麗瑤游說她報警。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥下午出席一個公開場合時回應稱對事件感到憤怒，稱自己曾看過呂表發的文章，明白對方公開事件前必經過一番內心掙扎，對呂願意講出事件經過而鼓掌，亦非常敬佩她的勇氣，希望呂的勇氣能喚醒社會對保護兒童的關注，亦能感染到曾遭受同樣不幸的人能勇於講出自己的經歷，強調執法機構會嚴肅跟進。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭稱已聯絡過警務處處長盧偉聰，要求警方盡可能跟進調查。其後警方派員到培正中學調查事件，但沒有透露任何調查情況。她亦指，警方要調查同類個案時必須得到受害人舉報，呼籲受害人即使不想再記起事件，都要鼓起勇氣舉報和提供資料協助警方調查。林鄭又指，即使呂不願與警方接觸，但她已在網上披露施害者的身份，相信學校亦有資料可以提供，但暫不便評論執法部門會採取甚麼跟進工作。<br />\n<br />\n她指政府會不停完善能頻繁接觸小朋友的求職者背景調查機制，但任何一個社會都難以完全避免同類事件，呼籲受害人無論事件已發生多久，都要鼓起勇氣，挺身而出，目前亦有機制保護受害人的身份不會被披露。林鄭又稱，任何人都應時刻保持警覺關心和保護小朋友，從事相關行業的人亦要「問問自己良心，小朋友對佢尊敬、信任佢，點可以做出呢啲令人非常之憤怒嘅行為？」<br />\n<br />\n警方消息解釋，雖然警方責任調查所有刑事案件，但若無任何人舉報或出現其他證據，如屍體或破壞物件等，警方很難展開調查，故必須獲受害人或相關人士合作。至於體育、演藝、文化及出版界立法會議員馬逢國提及自己收到另一宗涉及體育界的性侵指控，據悉警方亦會主動派人聯絡馬逢國了解詳情。 <br />\n<br />\n轉自香港蘋果日報網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171130/57524127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F57524127&d=3MzjoYWa7%2FEWPGoD32bGPTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a6e07fc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F57524127&h=5febd3dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171130/57524127</a>"},{"pid":"d106f3e03f346fc212b22c502d4ff27850db26fe","tid":485052,"uid":68094,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:21:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb3e59e46c0f4cd0be2ad122b182c50ae59f7d4d","tid":485052,"uid":140762,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"我明白被人侵犯係會好唔開心好傷心<br />\n但呂麗瑤又要出post但又唔同警方合作，究竟係想點？"},{"pid":"671f81c03f47467ab1f23f9777ed9b849433985b","tid":485052,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又唔post link，班盲撚又會屌關愛座兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n==<br />\n【體壇性侵】警下午抵培正搜集資料 林鄭籲呂麗瑤報警<br />\n最後更新: 1130 18:52 / 建立時間 (HKT): 1130 15:56<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171130/large/1512040517_4946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171130%2Flarge%2F1512040517_4946.jpg&h=d6b112e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171130/large/1512033200_ac90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171130%2Flarge%2F1512033200_ac90.jpg&h=3469bb58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（馬泉崇攝 ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171130/large/1512032464_00ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171130%2Flarge%2F1512032464_00ab.jpg&h=b51af761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（馬泉崇攝 ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【新增影片】<br />\n港隊「欄后」呂麗瑤在網上自爆中學時曾遭校隊教練性侵，警方下午派人到呂的母校培正中學，四名便裝探員到場後，未有回應記者提問。據悉，警方今日已間接接觸過呂麗瑤，但她婉拒與警方合作。消息指，由於這宗懷疑性侵案暫無任何人證物證或環境證據，警方需當事人合作舉報才可展開調查，故會繼續派人嘗試聯絡呂麗瑤游說她報警。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥下午出席一個公開場合時回應稱對事件感到憤怒，稱自己曾看過呂表發的文章，明白對方公開事件前必經過一番內心掙扎，對呂願意講出事件經過而鼓掌，亦非常敬佩她的勇氣，希望呂的勇氣能喚醒社會對保護兒童的關注，亦能感染到曾遭受同樣不幸的人能勇於講出自己的經歷，強調執法機構會嚴肅跟進。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭稱已聯絡過警務處處長盧偉聰，要求警方盡可能跟進調查。其後警方派員到培正中學調查事件，但沒有透露任何調查情況。她亦指，警方要調查同類個案時必須得到受害人舉報，呼籲受害人即使不想再記起事件，都要鼓起勇氣舉報和提供資料協助警方調查。林鄭又指，即使呂不願與警方接觸，但她已在網上披露施害者的身份，相信學校亦有資料可以提供，但暫不便評論執法部門會採取甚麼跟進工作。<br />\n<br />\n她指政府會不停完善能頻繁接觸小朋友的求職者背景調查機制，但任何一個社會都難以完全避免同類事件，呼籲受害人無論事件已發生多久，都要鼓起勇氣，挺身而出，目前亦有機制保護受害人的身份不會被披露。林鄭又稱，任何人都應時刻保持警覺關心和保護小朋友，從事相關行業的人亦要「問問自己良心，小朋友對佢尊敬、信任佢，點可以做出呢啲令人非常之憤怒嘅行為？」<br />\n<br />\n警方消息解釋，雖然警方責任調查所有刑事案件，但若無任何人舉報或出現其他證據，如屍體或破壞物件等，警方很難展開調查，故必須獲受害人或相關人士合作。至於體育、演藝、文化及出版界立法會議員馬逢國提及自己收到另一宗涉及體育界的性侵指控，據悉警方亦會主動派人聯絡馬逢國了解詳情。 <br />\n<br />\n轉自香港蘋果日報網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171130/57524127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F57524127&d=3MzjoYWa7%2FEWPGoD32bGPTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a6e07fc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F57524127&h=5febd3dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171130/57524127</a></blockquote><br />\nthank you thanky you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb25352a08630ad09876e930096aab6e8c32726","tid":485052,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又唔post link，班盲撚又會屌關愛座兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n==<br />\n【體壇性侵】警下午抵培正搜集資料 林鄭籲呂麗瑤報警<br />\n最後更新: 1130 18:52 / 建立時間 (HKT): 1130 15:56<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171130/large/1512040517_4946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171130%2Flarge%2F1512040517_4946.jpg&h=d6b112e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171130/large/1512033200_ac90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171130%2Flarge%2F1512033200_ac90.jpg&h=3469bb58&s={SIZE}\" /